  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is an expansion of a previous study done to determine how thinking skills relate
      to hypoglycemia (low blood sugar) and certain regions of the brain in children and
      adolescents. In this study, the investigators are testing thinking skills and measuring brain
      activity in adolescents with and without type 1 diabetes mellitus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
